DataElement.preferredName: Clinical Performed Observation Outcome Data ACT I2B2 CDM Laboratory Result Original Value
DataElement.preferredDefinition: Relating to the examination and treatment of patients dependent on direct observation.  The term may also refer to the institution (clinic) providing this activity.:Executed and carried through to completion.:Watching something and taking note of what happens.:The result of an action._A collection or single item of factual information, derived from measurement or research, from which conclusions may be drawn._The original test result value as seen in your source data. Values may include a decimal point, a sign or text (e.g., POSITIVE, NEGATIVE, DETECTED). The symbols >, <, >=, <= should be removed from the value and stored in the Modifier variable instead.
